data.description: This 3/2 open-concept home on a corner lot has been fully remodeled top to bottom and is a modern lovers dream. Some features include elegant quartz counter tops, tiled showers, black and white accents, and beautiful vinyl floors. The primary suite has not one but two closets and an en-suite bathroom including double sinks and a walk-in shower. On the other side of the home are two primary bedrooms not lacking in size and a secondary bathroom including a tub, shower, and double sinks. Outback you will find the covered patio overlooking a massive yard which includes a newly installed storage shed. If modern luxury is what you are looking for, you do not want to pass this one up! NEW ROOF Installed September 2023.
